item.title: Someone please please please help me!
item.dc:creator: @IP1 IP
item.description:
@IP1 wrote:

It’s because you don’t have a cache folder inside the client. Try downloading one, or download a client that has a cache folder. OR, if you have another client on your PC, copy the cache folder from that into the folder containing the files of the client that you are currently using. If that doesn’t work, post again.
